trans-unit.source: Manages the creation of the user profile and profile events.
trans-unit.target: Administrerer oppretting av brukerprofil og profilen hendelser.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: When the user profile is enabled, ASP.NET uses the ProfileModule to create the user profile and store it in the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Profile%2A> property of the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>.
trans-unit.target: Når profilen er aktivert, bruker ASP.NET ProfileModule til å opprette brukerprofilen og lagre den i <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Profile%2A>egenskapen for gjeldende <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>.</xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Profile%2A>

trans-unit.source: The ProfileModule exposes the following events you can handle to configure authentication in your application: - The <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.MigrateAnonymous> event, to migrate profile settings from an anonymous profile to an authenticated profile when an anonymous user logs in.
trans-unit.target: ProfileModule viser følgende hendelser kan du behandle for å konfigurere godkjenning i programmet:- <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.MigrateAnonymous>hendelsen for å overføre profilinnstillingene fra en anonym profilen til en godkjent profilen når en anonym bruker logger inn</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.MigrateAnonymous>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize> event, to customize how the user profile is created.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>Hendelsen for å tilpasse hvordan brukerprofilen er opprettet.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving> event, to control how the user profile is saved when the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileManager.AutomaticSaveEnabled%2A> property is set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving>Hendelsen for å styre hvordan brukerprofilen lagres når det <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileManager.AutomaticSaveEnabled%2A>er satt til `true`.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileManager.AutomaticSaveEnabled%2A> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving>

trans-unit.source: For information about enabling the user profile, see [profile Element (ASP.NET Settings Schema)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/ccb9bf3a-a044-464d-b89b-5cb5a3d389dd).
trans-unit.target: Du finner informasjon om hvordan du aktiverer brukerprofilen [profilopplysninger elementet (ASP.NET innstillingsskjemaet)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/ccb9bf3a-a044-464d-b89b-5cb5a3d389dd).

trans-unit.source: The current application.
trans-unit.target: Dette programmet.

trans-unit.source: Occurs when the anonymous user for a profile logs in.
trans-unit.target: Forekommer når en anonym bruker for en profil logger på.

trans-unit.source: You can access the MigrateAnonymous event of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> class in the Global.asax file for your ASP.NET application by using the `Profile_MigrateAnonymous` global event, as shown in the example for this topic.
trans-unit.target: Du har tilgang til hendelsen MigrateAnonymous for den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>klassen i filen Global.asax for ASP.NET-programmet ved hjelp av den `Profile_MigrateAnonymous` globale hendelse, som vist i eksemplet for dette emnet.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>

trans-unit.source: You can use the MigrateAnonymous event to copy profile property values from an anonymous profile to an authenticated profile when a user who has been anonymously using your application logs in.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke hendelsen MigrateAnonymous for å kopiere profilegenskapsverdier fra en anonym profilen til en godkjent profil når en bruker som har brukt anonymt programmet logger på.

trans-unit.source: When an application that has the user profile enabled is started, ASP.NET creates a new class of type `ProfileCommon`, which inherits from the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileBase> class.
trans-unit.target: Når et program som har brukerprofilen aktivert startes, ASP.NET oppretter en ny klasse av typen `ProfileCommon`, som arver fra <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileBase>klasse.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileBase>

trans-unit.source: Strongly typed accessors are added to the `ProfileCommon` class for each property defined in the configuration section.
trans-unit.target: Forespørselsparameter av sterk type aksessorer er lagt til i `ProfileCommon` klasse for hver egenskap som er definert i konfigurasjonsdelen.

trans-unit.source: A `GetProfile` method enables you to retrieve a `ProfileCommon` object based on a user name.
trans-unit.target: En `GetProfile` gjør det mulig å hente en `ProfileCommon` objekt basert på et brukernavn.

trans-unit.source: You can use the `GetProfile` method of the current, authenticated profile to retrieve the property values of the anonymous profile.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke den `GetProfile` metoden for den gjeldende, godkjente profilen til henter egenskapsverdier for anonym profilen.

trans-unit.source: The anonymous property values can then be copied to the current profile for the authenticated user.
trans-unit.target: Deretter kan kopieres anonym egenskapsverdiene for gjeldende profil for den godkjente brukeren.

trans-unit.source: Occurs before the user profile is created.
trans-unit.target: Forekommer før brukerprofilen er opprettet.

trans-unit.source: The Personalize event is raised during the <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AcquireRequestState?displayProperty=fullName> event.
trans-unit.target: Tilpass denne hendelsen oppstår under den <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AcquireRequestState?displayProperty=fullName>hendelsen.</xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AcquireRequestState?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You can access the Personalize event of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> class in the Global.asax file for your ASP.NET application using the `Profile_Personalize` global event as shown in the example for this topic.
trans-unit.target: Du har tilgang til hendelsen Tilpass for den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>klassen i filen Global.asax for din ASP.NET programmet ved hjelp av den `Profile_Personalize` globale hendelse som vises i eksemplet for dette emnet.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>

trans-unit.source: You can use the Personalize event to specify a custom user profile.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke hendelsen Tilpass til å angi en egendefinert brukerprofil.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs.Profile%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property value specified for the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventHandler> event handler for the Personalize event is set to a value that is not `null` when the Personalize event ends, then the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> will use the specified value of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs.Profile%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property as the value of the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Profile%2A> property of the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs.Profile%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapsverdien som er angitt for den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventHandler>hendelsesbehandling for Tilpass-handlingen er satt til en verdi som ikke er `null` når Tilpass hendelsen endene, og <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>vil bruke den angitte verdien for <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs.Profile%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen som verdien for <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Profile%2A>egenskapen for gjeldende <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>.</xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Profile%2A> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs.Profile%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventHandler> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs.Profile%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Occurs at the end of page execution if automatic profile saving is enabled.
trans-unit.target: Forekommer på slutten av siden kjøring hvis automatisk profilen lagring er aktivert.

trans-unit.source: The ProfileAutoSaving event is raised at the end of page execution if the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileManager.AutomaticSaveEnabled%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property is `true`.
trans-unit.target: ProfileAutoSaving denne hendelsen oppstår på slutten av siden kjøring hvis den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileManager.AutomaticSaveEnabled%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen `true`.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileManager.AutomaticSaveEnabled%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You can access the ProfileAutoSaving event of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> class in the Global.asax file for your ASP.NET application using the `Profile_ProfileAutoSaving` global event, as shown in the example for this topic.
trans-unit.target: Du har tilgang til hendelsen ProfileAutoSaving for den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>klassen i filen Global.asax for din ASP.NET programmet ved hjelp av den `Profile_ProfileAutoSaving` globale hendelse, som vist i eksemplet for dette emnet.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.SettingsBase.Save%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method checks the <xref:System.Configuration.SettingsPropertyValue.IsDirty%2A> property value for each <xref:System.Configuration.SettingsPropertyValue> in the user profile to determine whether properties that are made up of primitive types, strings, or <xref:System.DateTime> objects have been changed.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Configuration.SettingsBase.Save%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden sjekker den <xref:System.Configuration.SettingsPropertyValue.IsDirty%2A>egenskapsverdien for hver <xref:System.Configuration.SettingsPropertyValue>profilen å fastslå om egenskapene som består av primitive typer, strenger, eller <xref:System.DateTime>objekter er endret.</xref:System.DateTime> </xref:System.Configuration.SettingsPropertyValue> </xref:System.Configuration.SettingsPropertyValue.IsDirty%2A> </xref:System.Configuration.SettingsBase.Save%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.SettingsBase.Save%2A> method cannot explicitly determine whether a custom class has changed.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Configuration.SettingsBase.Save%2A>metoden eksplisitt kan ikke avgjøre om en egendefinert klasse er endret.</xref:System.Configuration.SettingsBase.Save%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can use the ProfileAutoSaving event to determine whether a custom object has been changed and then either to continue with the automatic save for modified objects or to cancel the automatic save if no objects have been modified.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke hendelsen ProfileAutoSaving å finne ut om et egendefinert objekt er endret, og lagre enten fortsette med automatisk for objekter som er endret eller avbryte automatisk lagring Hvis ingen objekter er endret.

trans-unit.source: To cancel the automatic profile save operation, set the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A> property to `false` in the ProfileAutoSaving event; otherwise, set the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A> property to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil avbryte automatisk profilen lagringen, angitt i <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A>egenskapen `false` i hendelsen ProfileAutoSaving; ellers satt i <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A>egenskapen `true`.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A>

trans-unit.source: There may be multiple subscribers to the ProfileAutoSaving event.
trans-unit.target: Det kan være flere abonnenter ProfileAutoSaving-hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> will use the last value that the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A> property is set to.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>vil bruke sist verdien som den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A>er satt til.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>

trans-unit.source: As a result, it is recommended that you explicitly set the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A> property in the ProfileAutoSaving event whether you are canceling or continuing with the automatic save, as you may need to overwrite the value set by an earlier subscriber.
trans-unit.target: Resultatet anbefales det at du har angitt den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A>egenskapen i hendelsen ProfileAutoSaving om du avbryter eller fortsetter med automatisk lagre, må du kanskje overskrive verdien som er angitt av en tidligere abonnenten.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A>
